name: ME24601
text:
Yes. DC has been holding back on announcing new titles until after Forever Evil ended. So far they have announced three new ongoings:

* Sinestro by Cullen Bunn with art by Dale Eaglesham
* Aquaman and the Others by Dan Jurgens with art by Lan Medina and Ed Tadeo 
* Secret Origins by a rotating team of writers

They also announced the cancellation of Teen Titans today.
